### Test Purchase API

### 1. Get all purchases
GET http://localhost:5000/api/purchases
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Create purchase in USD
POST http://localhost:5000/api/purchases/bulk-create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "supplierId": 1,
  "currencyId": 2,
  "paymentStatusId": 1,
  "totalAmount": 500.00,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 10,
      "unitPrice": 30.00,
      "totalPrice": 300.00
    },
    {
      "productId": 2,
      "quantity": 5,
      "unitPrice": 40.00,
      "totalPrice": 200.00
    }
  ]
}

